4. Technical Implementation
4.1 Tech Stack
Table
Layer	Technology	Rationale
Framework	Next.js 14 (App Router)	SSR, SEO, performance
Language	TypeScript	Type safety
Styling	Tailwind CSS + CSS Modules	Rapid development
UI Components	Radix UI (headless)	Accessibility, customization
Animation	Framer Motion	React-native animations
3D/WebGL	Three.js + React Three Fiber	Landing page visuals
Maps	Mapbox GL JS	Performance, custom styling
Charts	D3.js + Recharts	Data visualization
State	Zustand	Lightweight, no boilerplate
Real-time	Socket.io-client	WebSocket connections
Icons	Lucide React	Consistent, customizable
4.2 Performance Targets
Table
Metric	Target	Measurement
First Contentful Paint	<1.5s	Lighthouse
Time to Interactive	<3.5s	Lighthouse
3D Frame Rate	60fps	Chrome DevTools
Bundle Size	<200KB initial	Webpack Analyzer
API Response	<200ms	Server timing
